<!-- FEATURE IMAGES -->
<section class="feature-full" style="min-height:85vh"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/01_20241021110811A098_20250526152302A083_20250609174854A272.jpg" alt="X55 II RHD Exterior"><div class="feature-overlay"><h3 data-i18n="x55iirhd.vogueBeastDesign">Vogue Beast Design</h3><p data-i18n="x55iirhd.vogueBeastDesignDesc">The X55 II carries BAIC's Capital Beauty design language into the SUV segment. Bold, dynamic lines with a powerful stance create a strong visual presence on the road.</p></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-side"><div class="feature-side-img"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2023/02/23/21_20240708122129A015.jpg" alt="Interior"></div><div class="feature-side-content"><h3 data-i18n="x55iirhd.refinedInterior">Refined Interior</h3><p data-i18n="x55iirhd.refinedInteriorDesc">Dual 10-inch screens — LCD instrument cluster and central infotainment display. Apple CarPlay and EasyConnection mobile connectivity. Dual-zone automatic climate control with PM2.5 air purification and integrated refrigerator in the central armrest area.</p></div></div></section>

<section class="feature-full" style="min-height:80vh"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2023/02/23/22_20240708122153A018.jpg" alt="Dashboard"><div class="feature-overlay"><h3 data-i18n="x55iirhd.digitalCockpit">Digital Cockpit</h3><p data-i18n="x55iirhd.digitalCockpitDesc">10-inch LCD instrument screen paired with 10-inch central control display. Multi-color interior ambient lighting creates an immersive driving atmosphere. Voice control and wireless charging available on Luxury trim.</p></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-duo"><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2023/02/23/23_20240708122230A021.jpg" alt="Detail"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4 data-i18n="x55iirhd.hiddenDoorHandle">Hidden Door Handle</h4><p data-i18n="x55iirhd.hiddenDoorHandleDesc">Mechanical on Honor/Premium, inductive on Luxury trim</p></div></div><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/03改_20241021110831A100_20250526152334A088_20250609174930A277.jpg" alt="Wheels"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4 data-i18n="x55iirhd.alloyWheels">18"/19" Alloy Wheels</h4><p data-i18n="x55iirhd.alloyWheelsDesc">225/60 R18 two-tone on Honor/Premium, 225/55 R19 gray on Luxury</p></div></div></div></section>

<section class="feature-full" style="min-height:80vh"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/6_20230616111248A204_20250609145019A181_20250613152102A342.webp" alt="Safety"><div class="feature-overlay"><h3 data-i18n="x55iirhd.comprehensiveSafety">Comprehensive Safety</h3><p data-i18n="x55iirhd.comprehensiveSafetyDesc">ESP, ABS+EBD, EBA, HAC, HDC, and BOS brake override system. Driver and passenger airbags standard across all trims. Side airbags and air curtains on Premium and Luxury. TPMS tire pressure monitoring on all models.</p></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-side" style="direction:rtl"><div class="feature-side-img" style="direction:ltr"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2023/02/23/26_20240708122346A031.jpg" alt="Seats"></div><div class="feature-side-content" style="direction:ltr"><h3 data-i18n="x55iirhd.comfortSeating">Comfort Seating</h3><p data-i18n="x55iirhd.comfortSeatingDesc">Leather seats on Luxury trim with 6-way electric driver adjustment, memory, welcome function, and 4-way lumbar support. Front seat heating and ventilation. Rear seat angle adjustable on Luxury. Microfiber steering wheel on Honor and Premium.</p></div></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-duo"><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/8_20230223174141A161_20250609145055A186.jpg" alt="Intelligence"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4 data-i18n="x55iirhd.intelligentDriving">Intelligent Driving</h4><p data-i18n="x55iirhd.intelligentDrivingDesc">ACC adaptive cruise, AEB, BSD, LDW, FCW, LKA, HMA on Luxury</p></div></div><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/05_20241021110847A102_20250526152601A095_20250609174939A278.jpg" alt="Panoramic"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4 data-i18n="x55iirhd.panoramicSunroof">Panoramic Sunroof</h4><p data-i18n="x55iirhd.panoramicSunroofDesc">Available on Premium and Luxury trims with roof rack</p></div></div></div></section>

